title: GIRL TALK: acne, insecurities & hangovers
itunes:title: GIRL TALK: acne, insecurities & hangovers
description:
Brooke and Danielle are having another girl talk today and talking about some subjects they haven’t yet taken a deep dive into.  The gals discuss their biggest tips and battles with acne, some recent insecurities, and how they handle hangovers. Which hangover is worse, moral or physical?  Let the gals know if you enjoyed this girl talk episode by tagging @galsonthegopodcast on Instagram!
